{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6960b486df","title":"对《恐“敌”病一例》的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"08cca68ad3","index":0,"year":1962,"month":10,"day":8,"articleId":"6960b486df"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji45","name":"毛泽东全集第45卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/45-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji45":{"comments":[{"id":"798846f6ab","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"6960b486df","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共中央办公厅1962年10月4日编印的《情况简报》第348号上登载的《恐“敌”病一例》材料。材料说，据黑龙江省北安市委宣传部反映，今年8月间，该市双泉公社党委书记邱玉林夜间鸣枪赶狼，当地许多社、队干部和社员群众，听到枪声后误认为“敌人攻来”，惊恐万分，纷纷逃避。这种“精神状态”很值得注意。"},{"id":"cc4eb43287","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"6960b486df","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘，指刘少奇。周，指周恩来。朱，指朱德。邓，指邓小平，当时任中共中央总书记、国务院副总理。瑞卿，即罗瑞卿，当时任中共中央书记处书记、国务院副总理、中国人民解放军总参谋长。富治，即谢富治，当时任公安部部长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"6b0c5c924a","type":"title","text":"对《恐“敌”病一例》“的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"6960b486df"},{"id":"798846f6ab","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、周、朱、邓、瑞卿、富治同志阅。此事拟在常委会上谈一谈。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"6960b486df"},{"id":"cc4eb43287","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"6960b486df"},{"id":"6fd8eaf818","type":"paragraph","text":"十月八日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"6960b486df"},{"id":"7dfdeeada7","type":"paragraph","text":"阅后退毛。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"6960b486df"}],"page":{"id":"676d6b7baf","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"6960b486df","start":286,"end":286}}}},"__N_SSG":true}